<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP21_ProjectGold_UnityAndValues" s="488445">
  <T n="category">488441<!--TutorialCategory: tutorial_Category_EP21_ProjectGold--></T>
  <T n="name">0xD932DB42<!--String: "Unity Stability & Crisis"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Unity1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:6fcfabce318d0186</T>
      <T n="text">0x88D90547<!--String: "A Dynasty's <b><font color='#199C2C'>Unity</font></b> represents how well everyone in the Dynasty is <b><font color='#199C2C'>getting along</font></b>. When relationships in the Dynasty are <b><font color='#199C2C'>strong</font></b>, Unity will reach <b><font color='#199C2C'>Stability</font></b>, but when they are <b><font color='#199C2C'>weak or outright hostile</font></b>, a Unity <b><font color='#199C2C'>Crisis</font></b> becomes inevitable.\n\nDuring Unity Stability, Members will <b><font color='#199C2C'>build friendships</font></b> with each other quicker and more successfully. \n\nIn a Crisis, the Members will <b><font color='#199C2C'>struggle to get along</font></b>, and build relationships slower. Some Members may even make <b><font color='#199C2C'>demands</font></b> of the Dynasty Head, or <b><font color='#199C2C'>threaten to leave</font></b>!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Unity2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:6fcfabce318d0185</T>
      <T n="text">0x9EF9C773<!--String: "Spending <b><font color='#199C2C'>quality time together</font></b> is the best way to build Unity, but there are some tricks! Influential Dynasty Members can <b><font color='#199C2C'>Encourage</font></b> Members to befriend each other, and the Dynasty Head can choose <b><font color='#199C2C'>Perks</font></b> that make building friendships easier. Worst comes to worst, if there is a Member who doesn't get along with anyone, the Head can just <b><font color='#199C2C'>throw them out</font></b>!\n\nIt's important for a Dynasty Head to remember that certain actions, such as Excluding a Member or changing a Dynasty Value, may <b><font color='#199C2C'>upset many Members</font></b>. This can quickly lead to a Crisis! <b><font color='#199C2C'>Avoid unpopular decisions</font></b> or make sure to <b><font color='#199C2C'>mend damaged relationships</font></b> to avoid catastrophe."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
